      "body" : "I thought of using Character.isDigit() myself, but it also accepts some characters that are not 0-9 (see docs: <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/Character.html#isDigit%28char%29\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/&hellip;</a> )"
