    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using Google Guava:</p>\n\n<pre><code>CharMatcher.inRange('0','9').retainFrom(\"123-456-789\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>UPDATE:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Using <a href=\"http://guava-libraries.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/javadoc/com/google/common/base/CharMatcher.html#precomputed()\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Precomputed CharMatcher</a> can further improve performance</p>\n\n<pre><code>CharMatcher ASCII_DIGITS=CharMatcher.inRange('0','9').precomputed();  \nASCII_DIGITS.retainFrom(\"123-456-789\");\n</code></pre>\n"
